# ============================================
# RAZORPAY CONFIGURATION (For Payments)
# ============================================
# Get these from https://dashboard.razorpay.com/app/dashboard
# 1. Sign up/Login to Razorpay
# 2. Go to Settings > API Keys
# 3. Generate Test keys (or Live keys for production)
# 4. Copy the Key ID and Key Secret here
